sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Pingora
    participant L0
    
    Note over Client,L0: Scenario: Hot cache (L0 HIT)<br/>Fastest possible path
    
    Client->>Pingora: GET /image.jpg
    activate Pingora
    
    Pingora->>L0: lookup(key)
    activate L0
    L0-->>Pingora: HIT (meta, handler)
    deactivate L0
    
    Note over Pingora: No wrapper needed<br/>No promotions from L0<br/>Pure in-process memory serving
    
    loop Stream from L0
        Pingora->>L0: read_body()
        activate L0
        L0-->>Pingora: chunk
        deactivate L0
        Pingora-->>Client: chunk
    end
    
    Pingora->>L0: finish()
    activate L0
    L0-->>Pingora: ok
    deactivate L0
    
    Pingora-->>Client: complete
    deactivate Pingora
    
    Note over Client,L0: Total overhead: ~microseconds<br/>No network, no async tasks<br/>No allocations beyond chunk buffer<br/>No trait indirection (in-process cache)
